        <mxCell id="9" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" value="&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left; font-size: 12px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.6;&#39;&gt;&lt;b&gt;• File Name:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;font color=&#39;#1B365D&#39;&gt;problem1.mat&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;• Problem ID (w):&lt;/b&gt; 2&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;• Number of Jobs (N):&lt;/b&gt; 8&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;• Number of Machines (M):&lt;/b&gt; 5&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;• Total PM Activities (Z_total):&lt;/b&gt; 3&lt;br/&gt;  (Machine 1: 1, M2: 0, M3: 1, M4: 1, M5: 0)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;• Total Sequence Length (CL):&lt;/b&gt; 11&lt;br/&gt;  &lt;font color=&#39;#475569&#39;&gt;Formula: CL = N + Z_total = 8 + 3 = 11&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;• Tardiness Factor (TF):&lt;/b&gt; 0.4004&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;• Relative Due Date Range (RD):&lt;/b&gt; 0.40&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;• Mean Due Date (&amp;mu;&lt;sub&gt;DD&lt;/sub&gt;):&lt;/b&gt; 12540.59&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;• Due Date Range (R&lt;sub&gt;DD&lt;/sub&gt;):&lt;/b&gt; 8366.14&lt;br/&gt;  &lt;font color=&#39;#475569&#39;&gt;Formula &amp;mu;&lt;sub&gt;DD&lt;/sub&gt;: &amp;Sigma;(&amp;mu;&lt;sub&gt;p&lt;/sub&gt;)/N * M * N * (1-TF)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br/&gt;  &lt;font color=&#39;#475569&#39;&gt;Formula R&lt;sub&gt;DD&lt;/sub&gt;: &amp;Sigma;(&amp;mu;&lt;sub&gt;p&lt;/sub&gt;)/N * M * N * RD&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;hr style=&#39;border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CBD5E1;&#39;/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Infographic Concepts Illustrated:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• Blue cells represent input parameters.&lt;br/&gt;• Grey cells represent raw matrix values.&lt;br/&gt;• Arrows represent mathematical linkages.&lt;br/&gt;• Stacked grids represent 3D tensors.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="420" width="290" x="65" y="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="10" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;align=left;" value="&lt;div style=&#39;font-size: 11px; color: #475569; text-align: left;&#39;&gt;Cell &lt;b&gt;TPO(k, i)&lt;/b&gt; is the processing time of &lt;b&gt;Job i&lt;/b&gt; on &lt;b&gt;Machine k&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;Size: 5 rows (Machines) &amp;times; 8 columns (Jobs).&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="560" x="420" y="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
