        <mxCell id="238" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" value="&lt;div style=&#39;font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.5; text-align: left; color: #78350F;&#39;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. Machine Aging Model:&lt;/b&gt; As Machine &lt;i&gt;k&lt;/i&gt; processes Job &lt;i&gt;i&lt;/i&gt;, its age increases by &lt;i&gt;TPO(k, i)&lt;/i&gt;. The machine&#39;s failure rate follows a Weibull distribution with shape &amp;beta; and scale &amp;eta;.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;2. Planned Maintenance (PM):&lt;/b&gt; To prevent failure, a PM is scheduled. A PM is performed once the accumulated age of Machine &lt;i&gt;k&lt;/i&gt; reaches the threshold &lt;i&gt;v&lt;sub&gt;k&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/i&gt; (e.g., 428.5 on M1). PM restores the machine age to 0.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;3. Stochastic Breakdowns &amp; Corrective Maintenance (CM):&lt;/b&gt; If the machine fails before reaching &lt;i&gt;v&lt;sub&gt;k&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/i&gt;, a CM is performed (taking duration &lt;i&gt;R&lt;sub&gt;k&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/i&gt;), restoring the machine age to 0.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;4. Total Schedule length (CL=11):&lt;/b&gt; Composed of 8 Job Orders + 3 PM slots = 11 positions. The metaheuristic schedules the sequence of these 11 elements to minimize ETP.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="150" width="530" x="1055" y="1000" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="239" edge="1" parent="1" source="19" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;strokeColor=#4F46E5;strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;" target="189" value="Sum of row values = P_k">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <Array as="points">
              <mxPoint x="400" y="235" />
              <mxPoint x="400" y="80" />
              <mxPoint x="1010" y="80" />
              <mxPoint x="1010" y="385" />
              <mxPoint x="1235" y="385" />
            </Array>
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="240" edge="1" parent="1" source="195" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;strokeColor=#16A34A;strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;" target="9" value="Sum(Z) = 3 PMs added to sequence">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
            <Array as="points">
              <mxPoint x="1270" y="420" />
              <mxPoint x="1270" y="490" />
